<h1>🚀 DEVELOPMENT VELOCITY & PROGRESS REPORT</h1>
<p style="text-align:center;"><strong>Project:</strong> Infinity Finance (LoanBrick) | <strong>Reporting Period:</strong> March 10 – 20, 2026</p>

<h2>📈 Velocity Overview</h2>
<p>The development cycle for the Infinity Finance LMS has broken internal records for speed and stability. In just 10 days, the platform transitioned from a blank slate to a fully-synced, encrypted financial ecosystem.</p>

<div class="metric-box">
    <p>Average Functional Delivery</p>
    <div class="metric-value">1.5 Modules / Day</div>
    <p>99.81% Unit & E2E Test Coverage</p>
</div>

