<h2>🛠 Strategic Success Factors</h2>
<h3>1. Automated Quality Assurance</h3>
<p>By leveraging an industry-leading <strong>99.81% test coverage</strong>, the project bypassed the traditional intensive bug-fixing phase, allowing for straight-line development velocity.</p>

<h3>2. Cloud-Native Synchronization</h3>
<p>The bidirectional sync architecture between the local device and Supabase Cloud allowed for near-instant deployment of new features without disrupting field data parity.</p>

<h3>3. Rapid Prototyping and Iteration</h3>
<p>Direct communication and rapid feedback loops resulted in a "95% complete" state within the first week of intensive engineering.</p>

